==制作==
{{quote box|width=30%|align=right|size=250px|quote=“我感觉很重要的一点是，第三部电影是一个[[时代|时代]]的结束，就像[[后现代主义|后现代主义]][[西部片|西部片]]那样，[[铁路|铁路]]铺就了，枪战也逐渐消失了。看起来我们有机会了解一下这个腐败横行，诚实无处容身的世界，让人感到阴暗和惆账，神话已是奄奄一息。这些看起来会是用来完成这三部曲的一个伟大主题。”|source=——高爾·韋賓斯基<ref>{{cite news |author=Ian Berriman |title=Gore Verbinski on Pirates of the Caribbean 3 |work=SFX magazine |date=2007-11-13 |url=http://www.sfx.co.uk/2007/11/13/gore_verbinski_on_pirates_of_the_caribbean_3/ |accessdate=2013-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130822100236/http://www.sfx.co.uk/2007/11/13/gore_verbinski_on_pirates_of_the_caribbean_3/ |archive-date=2013-08-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>}}

随着2003年《加勒比海盗：黑珍珠号的诅咒》所获得的巨大成功，主创和演员们决定签约同时拍摄两部续集<ref>{{cite news|author=Brian Linder |title=Back-to-Back Pirates |work=IGN |date=2003-10-21 |url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2003/10/21/back-to-back-pirates |accessdate=2013-08-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120118050811/http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/455/455825p1.html |archivedate=2012-01-18 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。导演高爾·韋賓斯基在第二部电影中为了让剧情获得发展而对角色作出了一些改变，他希望可以在第三部里恢复原有的基调<ref name="Empire">{{cite news |author=Ian Nathan |title=Pirates 3 |work=Empire |pages=88–92 |date=2007-04-27 |accessdate=2007-05-02}}</ref>。在现实生活中海盗联盟的启发下，特里·鲁西奥和泰德·艾略特根据历史人物在现有主要演员的基础上增加了一些虚构的角色<ref>{{cite web|title=Pirate Lords |work=Walt Disney Pictures |year=2007 |url=http://www.myspace.com/atworldsend |accessdate=2007-07-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070702232532/http://myspace.com/atworldsend |archivedate=2007-07-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。最后他们还在剧中引入了第一部电影里巴博沙船长所提及过的“异教徒之神”[[卡吕普索|卡吕普索]]<ref>{{cite news|author=Scott Holleran |title=Interview: Ted Elliott & Terry Rossio on 'At World's End' |work=Box Office Mojo |date=2007-05-31 |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/features/?id=2323&p=.htm |accessdate=2013-08-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130511212731/http://boxofficemojo.com/features/?id=2323&p=.htm |archivedate=2013-05-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

《加勒比海盗2：聚魂棺》的拍摄工作于2006年3月1日结束，第三部电影的部分镜头也是在同样的地点取景<ref>{{cite web|title=Chapter 7 - Return to The Bahamas |publisher=Production Notes |url=http://numberonestars.com/pirates3/production7.htm |accessdate=2013-08-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120509164220/http://numberonestars.com/pirates3/production7.htm |archivedate=2012-05-09 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。2005年8月拍摄[[新加坡|新加坡]]背景的桥段期间，剧组制作了许多外景拍摄所需要的大型道具，其中包括一个40米长，24米宽，1.1米深的水箱。由于18世纪的新加坡在纪录上并不完善，主创人员于是选择以同时期[[马来西亚|马来西亚]]和[[中国|中国]]的城市进行[[表现主义|表现派]]风格刻划。韋賓斯基还有意用片中城市的设定戏仿[[Spa|Spa]]文化，片场到处都生长着[[真菌|真菌]]。为了延续这种自然的感觉，嘯風澡堂的地板必须以手工进行切割，然后再在片场利用照明设备和数[[加仑|加仑]]的水来营造出较为真实的湿度效果<ref>{{cite news|title=Singapore Sling |publisher=Production Notes |url=http://numberonestars.com/pirates3/production6.htm |accessdate=2013-08-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120711193419/http://numberonestars.com/pirates3/production6.htm |archivedate=2012-07-11 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

电影的拍摄工作于2006年8月3日在[[犹他州|犹他州]]的[[巴纳维亚盐带平地|巴纳维亚盐带平地]]继续进行<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.ksl.com/?nid=148&sid=412952 |title=Captain Jack Sparrow Landed In Utah Last Week |work=KSL News |date=2006-08-09 |accessdate=2013-08-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120927010400/http://www.ksl.com/?nid=148&sid=412952 |archivedate=2012-09-27 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，一直持续到2007年初，需要在[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]地区摄制的镜头已经于2005年完成<ref>{{cite news|author=Jeff Otto |title=Pirates 3 Production Details |work=IGN |date=2006-06-28 |url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2006/06/28/pirates-3-production-details |accessdate=2013-08-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120311104405/http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/714/714895p1.html |archivedate=2012-03-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。困住杰克·斯派罗船长的那片戴夫·琼斯魔柜实际上是在犹他州拍摄的，摄影师利用单色镜头来营造一种和海盗通常五光十色的生活环境截然不同的感观<ref name="Deck">{{cite news|author=Noah Kadner |title=All Hands On Deck |work=American Cinematographer |date=June 2007 |url=http://www.ascmag.com/magazine_dynamic/June2007/Pirates3/page1.php# |accessdate=2009-04-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090411230334/http://www.ascmag.com/magazine_dynamic/June2007/Pirates3/page1.php%23 |archivedate=2009-04-11 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。电影高潮的大战是在[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[棕櫚谷_(加利福尼亞州)|棕櫚谷]]的一个机库摄制的<ref>{{cite news|author=Josh Rottenburg |title=Days of Plunder |work=Entertainment Weekly |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20038372,00.html |accessdate=2013-08-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121013125023/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20038372%2C00.html |archivedate=2012-10-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，一众演员不得不在服装内穿上雨衣。而经水淋湿的外景道具保存在冰冻温度下以确保不会滋生[[细菌|细菌]]感染剧组成员<ref>{{cite news|author=Sam Ashurst |title=Orlando and Keira: Uncut! |work=Total Film |date=2007-05-14 |url=http://www.totalfilm.com/features/keira_and_orlando_uncut! |accessdate=2008-06-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080609211017/http://www.totalfilm.com/features/keira_and_orlando_uncut%21 |archivedate=2008-06-09 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。此外，还有一个第二剧组在[[尼亚加拉瀑布|尼亚加拉瀑布]]进行拍摄<ref>{{cite news|title=Third ''Pirates'' filmed at Niagara Falls |work=ComingSoon.net |date=2006-10-30 |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=17265 |accessdate=2013-08-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121001064747/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=17265 |archivedate=2012-10-01 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。[[工业光魔公司|工业光魔公司]]为电影制作了750个特效镜头，[[数字领域公司|数字领域公司]]也制作了300个，这些特效镜头一共花了5个月的时间制作完成。影片在制作与水有关的特技镜头方面提出了诸多挑战<ref>{{cite news|author=Bill Desowitz |url=http://mag.awn.com/article_view.php?id=3311&site=vfxw&page=all |title=ILM Meets the Maelstrom on the Third ''Pirates'' |work=VFXWorld |date=2007-06-07 |accessdate=2007-06-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090411203744/http://mag.awn.com/article_view.php?id=3311&site=vfxw&page=all |archivedate=2009-04-11 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

电影的主体摄制工作于2006年12月12日在[[摩洛凱島|摩洛凱島]]完成<ref name="Aloha">{{cite news|title=Aloha Oe: Hawaii Farewell |publisher=Production Notes |url=http://numberonestars.com/pirates3/production17.htm |accessdate=2013-08-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130426200902/http://numberonestars.com/pirates3/production17.htm |archivedate=2013-04-26 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，起初剪辑完成的版本长度为3小时<ref name="Rossio">{{cite news|title=Exclusive Interview: Terry Rossio |work=Moviehole.net |date=2007-02-12 |url=http://www.moviehole.net/interviews/20070212_exclusive_interview_terry_ross.html |accessdate=2009-05-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071011163402/http://www.moviehole.net/interviews/20070212_exclusive_interview_terry_ross.html |archivedate=2007-10-11 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。之后的剪辑又剪去了20分钟的内容，不过制片人[[傑瑞·布洛克海默|傑瑞·布洛克海默]]保留了最后大战所需要的长时间准备内容<ref>{{cite news|title=Exclusive Interview: Jerry Bruckheimer |work=Moviehole.net |date=2007-05-21 |url=http://www.moviehole.net/interviews/20070521_exclusive_interview_jerry_bruc.html |accessdate=2009-05-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080623084730/http://www.moviehole.net/interviews/20070521_exclusive_interview_jerry_bruc.html |archivedate=2008-06-23 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

[[漢斯·季默|漢斯·季默]]继两部前作后继续为本片谱曲，他一共创作了8个新的主题，其中包括为本片原声带创作的一个[[爱情|爱情]]主题<ref name="Aloha" />。季默在电影开始剪辑的同时进行创作，所以对片中音乐的剪辑有一定的影响。高爾·韋賓斯基对作曲提供了帮助，他为片中多个镜头的音乐演奏了[[吉他|吉他]]<ref>{{cite video |title=The Pirate Maestro: The Music of Hans Zimmer |format=DVD |work=Buena Vista |year=2007}}</ref>，并且还和季默一起创作了片中的一首名为《{{lang|en|Hoist the Colours}}》的歌曲<ref>{{cite video |title=Hoist the Colors |format=DVD |work=Buena Vista |date=2007}}</ref>。

==发行==
[[Image:Keith_Richards.jpg|thumb]]

《加勒比海盗3：世界的尽头》的全球首映式于2007年5月19日在[[迪士尼樂園|迪士尼樂園]]举行，首映式还面向普通公众开放，门票价格为1500美元，这笔收入将汇入[[願望成真基金|願望成真基金]]用于[[慈善|慈善]]事业<ref>{{cite news |author=The Disneyland Report |title=Disneyland announces sale of Pirates of the Caribbean: At World's End premiere tickets |publisher=''DisneylandReport.com'' |date=2007-04-13 |url=http://www.disneylandreport.com/disneynews/070414-pirates-of-the-caribbean-at-worlds-end-premiere-tickets.html |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130321054828/http://www.disneylandreport.com/disneynews/070414-pirates-of-the-caribbean-at-worlds-end-premiere-tickets.html |archivedate=2013-03-21 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。就在几个星期前，[[华特迪士尼影片|华特迪士尼影片]]决定将电影的美国上映日期从2007年5月25日（[[星期五|星期五]]）提前到5月24日<ref>{{cite news|author=Dave McNary |title=Disney moves up 'Pirates' opening |publisher=''Variety'' |date=2007-05-08 |url=http://variety.com/2007/film/news/disney-moves-up-pirates-opening-1117964457/ |accessdate=2007-05-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070715100138/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117964457.html?categoryid=1236&cs=1 |archivedate=2007-07-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。电影首晚在美国的4362家电影院上映，打破了《[[蜘蛛人3|蜘蛛人3]]》所创下的在4253家电影院上映的纪录<ref name="records">{{cite news|author=Ian Mohr |url=http://variety.com/2007/film/news/spider-man-3-sets-records-2-1117964093/ |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121106155841/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117964093?refCatId=13 |archivedate=2012-11-06 |title='Spider-Man 3' sets records |publisher=''Variety'' |date=2007-05-01 |accessdate=2007-05-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Pirates Opens in Record # of Theaters |publisher=''ComingSoon.net'' |date=2007-05-24 |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=20628 |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121001064756/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=20628 |archivedate=2012-10-01 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，但这个成绩之后被《[[黑暗骑士|黑暗骑士]]》所超越<ref>{{cite news|author=Carl DiOrio |title=High expectations for 'Dark Knight' |work=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2008-07-16 |format=Registration required |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/high-expectations-dark-knight-115810 |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023215815/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/high-expectations-dark-knight-115810 |archivedate=2012-10-23 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=darkknight.htm |title=The Dark Knight (2008) |publisher=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130502035800/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=darkknight.htm |archivedate=2013-05-02 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|first=Carl |last=DiOrio |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/dark-knight-sells-quickly-online-115869 |title='Dark Knight' sells out quickly online |journal=The Hollywood Reporter |publisher=Nielsen Company |date=2008-07-17 |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080803142239/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/film/news/e3ic89034626f7645c385ca5977ca529ca2 |archivedate=2008-08-03 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

===营销===
经过一段低调的宣传活动后，电影的预告片于2007年在{{lang|en|ShowWest}}展会上[[首演|首映]]<ref>{{cite news|author=Edward Douglas |title=Disney Kicks Off ShoWest Opening Ceremony |publisher=''ComingSoon.net'' |date=2007-03-13 |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/blog/2007/03/disney_kicks_off_showest_openi.php |accessdate=2009-04-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090412061927/http://www.comingsoon.net/blog/2007/03/disney_kicks_off_showest_openi.php |archivedate=2009-04-12 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，首先是在2007年3月18日《加勒比海盗：黑珍珠号的诅咒》 一场名为“海盗极限影迷见面会”的特别放映活动中播映，再于3月19日和《[[与星共舞_(美国真人秀)|与星共舞]]》一起播映，之后再在[[互联网|互联网]]上发布<ref>{{cite news|author=Walt Disney Pictures |title=Pirates Trailer to Debut March 19! |publisher=''ComingSoon.net'' |date=2007-03-09 |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=19258 |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121001064816/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=19258 |archivedate=2012-10-01 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。[[国家娱乐收藏品协会|国家娱乐收藏品协会]]还在4月下旬发布了电影的动作玩偶<ref>{{cite news|author=Nisha Gopalan |title=First Look! Toy Fair '07 |publisher=''Entertainment Weekly'' |date=2007-02-09 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/gallery/0,,__20011142_1,00.html |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121013125031/http://www.ew.com/ew/gallery/0%2C%2C__20011142_1%2C00.html |archivedate=2012-10-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。此外还有珍藏版的[[國際象棋|國際象棋]]套装，[[地產大亨|地產大亨]]游戏，海盗主题的[[大话骰|大话骰]]之类的[[圖版遊戲|圖版遊戲]]发行，甚至还有片中人物的[[雕塑|雕塑]]和珠宝首饰的复制品<ref>{{cite news|author=Edward Douglas |title=Pirates of the Caribbean at Toy Fair '07! |publisher=''ComingSoon.net'' |date=2007-02-13 |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=18881 |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121001064824/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=18881 |archivedate=2012-10-01 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。2007年5月22日，一款同名[[电子游戏|电子游戏]]发行了[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]、[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]、[[Wii|Wii]]、[[PlayStation_Portable|PSP]]、[[PlayStation_2|PlayStation 2]]、[[个人电脑|PC]]和[[任天堂DS|任天堂DS]]多种格式版本<ref>{{cite news|author=Disney Interactive Studios |title=Pirates to Set Sail on Consoles and Handhelds |publisher=''ComingSoon.net'' |date=2007-03-19 |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=19425 |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121001064849/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=19425 |archivedate=2012-10-01 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。电影的同名原声带唱片也在5月22日发行<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.soundtrack.net/albums/database/?id=4465 |title=Soundtrack.Net : Pirates of the Caribbean: At World's End Soundtrack |publisher=Soundtrack.net |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130630073648/http://www.soundtrack.net/albums/database/?id=4465 |archivedate=2013-06-30 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

=== 电影审查 ===
至少有一个国家的官方[[审查制度|审查机构]]下令剪去电影的部分内容。据[[新华社|新华社]]报导，电影在[[中国大陆|中国大陆]]上映时有约10分钟周润发扮演新加坡海盗啸风的镜头被剪。在未经审查的国家放映时，周润发的出场时间有约20分钟。中国官方没有对这一审查行为的原因给出解释，但中国大陆的非官方来源表示镜头被剪的原因是这个角色对[[中国人|中国人]]存在一种负面而陈腐的形象写照<ref>{{cite news|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070702075304/http://www.cnn.com/2007/SHOWBIZ/Movies/06/15/china.pirates.ap/index.html |archivedate=2007-07-02 |title=China gives bald pirate the chop |publisher=Associated Press |date=2007-06-15 |url=http://www.cnn.com/2007/SHOWBIZ/Movies/06/15/china.pirates.ap/index.html |accessdate=2006-06-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

===家用媒体===
华特迪士尼家庭娱乐公司于2007年11月19日发行了电影的第二区单碟版和重新剪辑的双碟版[[DVD|DVD]]，两者都有标准DVD和[[蓝光光碟|蓝光光碟]]两种格式<ref>{{cite news|author=Walt Disney Pictures Home Entertainment |title=Pirates Hitting DVD and Blu-ray December 4 |work=ComingSoon.net |date=2007-07-26 |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=22800 |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121001064938/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=22800 |archivedate=2012-10-01 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。2007年11月21日又在[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]发行了DVD，12月4日再在美国和[[加拿大|加拿大]]发行。双碟限量版的DVD一直发行到了2008年9月30日截止，而包含所有双碟DVD版本内容的蓝光光碟（包括一些影院上映的原始内容，但不包括[[编剧|编剧]]的评论音轨）仍然在进行发售。起初的蓝光光碟包装盒的背面将高清制式误印为1080i，而迪士尼公司确认应该是[[1080p|1080p]]。最后该公司决定不再召回所有误印的版本，而只是在之后的产品中纠正这处失误<ref>{{cite web|title=Pirates Packaging Misprint |work=Blu-ray.com |url=http://www.blu-ray.com/news/?id=723 |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120225043634/http://www.blu-ray.com/news/?id=723 |archivedate=2012-02-25 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。DVD的市场销售带来了2亿9604万3871美元的收入，是2007年最畅销的，只是其实际销量（1450万5271套）实际上还是落后于《[[變形金剛_(2007年電影)|变形金刚]]》（1623万4195套）<ref name="The-Numbers">{{cite web|title=Pirates of the Caribbean: At World's End |work=The-Numbers.com |url=http://www.the-numbers.com/movies/2007/PIRT3.php |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130508081727/http://www.the-numbers.com/movies/2007/PIRT3.php |archivedate=2013-05-08 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

==反响==
===专业评价===
与《加勒比海盗2：聚魂棺》一样<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/pirates_of_the_caribbean_dead_mans_chest |title=Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Man's Chest (2006) |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130530140455/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/pirates_of_the_caribbean_dead_mans_chest/ |archivedate=2013-05-30 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/pirates-of-the-caribbean-dead-mans-chest |accessdate=2013-08-23 |publisher=Metacritic |title=Pirates of the Caribbean  Dead Man's Chest Reviews |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130121203451/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/pirates-of-the-caribbean-dead-mans-chest |archivedate=2013-01-21 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，《加勒比海盗3：世界的尽头》所获得的评价褒贬不一。根据[[烂蕃茄|烂蕃茄]]上所收集的225份评论文章来看，其中99份给出了“新鲜”的正面评价，“新鲜度”为44%，平均得分5.46（满分为10）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/pirates_of_the_caribbean_3 |title=Pirates of the Caribbean: At World's End Movie Reviews, Pictures |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130530065917/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/pirates_of_the_caribbean_3/ |archivedate=2013-05-30 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。而从[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上收集的36篇评论文章来看，其中12篇给出好评，5篇差评，19篇褒贬不一，平均得分50（满分100）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/pirates-of-the-caribbean-at-worlds-end |title=Pirates of the Caribbean: At World's End Reviews, Ratings, Credits |publisher=Metacritic |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025130746/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/pirates-of-the-caribbean-at-worlds-end |archivedate=2012-10-25 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。亚历克斯·比林顿（{{lang|en|Alex Billington}}）指出：“这正是当今电影业的运作方式，评论家给出负面的评价，而公众的看法通常又与之相反，但不管是哪一种情况，电影公司都有大把的钱可以赚。”<ref>{{cite news|author=Alex Billington |title=Get Ready for a Swarm of Negative Critics This Friday on Pirates 3 |publisher=FirstShowing.net |date=2007-05-22 |url=http://www.firstshowing.net/2007/get-ready-for-a-swarm-of-negative-critics-this-friday-on-pirates-3/ |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120722094409/http://www.firstshowing.net/2007/get-ready-for-a-swarm-of-negative-critics-this-friday-on-pirates-3/ |archivedate=2012-07-22 |deadurl=no }}</ref>

{{link-en|德鲁·麦克温尼|Drew McWeeny}}是少数给予本片正面评价的影评人之一，他称赞影片因其情节上的复杂性而有值得反复欣赏的价值，“这可能是其最精明的举措”<ref>{{cite news|author=Drew McWeeny |title=Moriarty Sets Sail With PIRATES 3: AT WORLD’S END! |publisher=''Ain't It Cool News'' |date=2007-05-24 |url=http://www.aintitcool.com/node/32783 |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120927174948/http://www.aintitcool.com/node/32783 |archivedate=2012-09-27 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。[[IGN|IGN]]网站的托德·吉尔克里斯特（{{lang|en|Todd Gilchrist}}）感觉电影的情况与像《[[星際大戰|星際大戰]]》之类的其它三部曲过于类似，但仍然称赞了其制作价值<ref>{{cite news|author=Todd Gilchrist |url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2007/11/15/pirates-of-the-caribbean-at-worlds-end-dvd-review |title=Pirates of the Caribbean: At World's End |publisher=IGN |date=2007-05-24 |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120311104413/http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/791/791309p1.html |archivedate=2012-03-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。《[[综艺|综艺]]》的布赖恩·洛瑞（{{lang|en|Brian Lowry}}）认为与去年臃肿的续集相比，本片至少内容上更充足，情节上更连贯，没有因长时间为压轴戏码作铺垫而让人感到麻木<ref>{{cite news|author=Brian Lowry |title=Pirates of the Caribbean: At World's End |publisher=''Variety'' |date=2007-05-22 |url=http://variety.com/2007/film/reviews/pirates-of-the-caribbean-at-world-s-end-3-1200559054/ |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070524060242/http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117933737.html?categoryid=31&cs=1 |archivedate=2007-05-24 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。{{link-en|全面电影|Total Film}}称赞了演员的表演，但批评过分的曲折和论述让人很难对角色产生感情<ref>{{cite news|title=Pirates Of The Caribbean: At World's End |publisher=''Total Film'' |url=http://www.totalfilm.com/cinema_reviews/films_out_this_week/pirates_of_the_caribbean_at_worlds_end |accessdate=2009-05-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070524075651/http://www.totalfilm.com/cinema_reviews/films_out_this_week/pirates_of_the_caribbean_at_worlds_end |archivedate=2007-05-24 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。爱德华·道格拉斯（{{lang|en|Edward Douglas}}）喜欢这部电影，但对其节奏感到不满<ref>{{cite news|author=Edward Douglas |title=Pirates of the Caribbean: At World's End |publisher=ComingSoon.net |date=2007-05-24 |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/reviewsnews.php?id=20555 |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121001064917/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/reviewsnews.php?id=20555 |archivedate=2012-10-01 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，而布莱克·怀特则批评了片中戴夫·琼斯魔柜和卡普吕索的桥段<ref>{{cite news|author=Blake Wright |title=Pirates of the Caribbean: At World's End |publisher=ComingSoon.net |date=2007-05-24 |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/reviewsnews.php?id=20611 |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121001064923/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/reviewsnews.php?id=20611 |archivedate=2012-10-01 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。{{link-en|詹姆斯·伯拉迪尼|James Berardinelli}}认为本片最后一个小时与前作相对有些脱节，而加勒比海盗三部曲在制作水准上也是参差不齐<ref>{{cite news|author=James Berardinelli|title=Pirates of the Caribbean: At World's End|publisher=''Reelviews''|year=2007|url=http://www.reelviews.net/movies/p/pirates_caribbean3.html|accessdate=2013-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120608143519/http://www.reelviews.net/movies/p/pirates_caribbean3.html|archive-date=2012-06-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[滾石_(雜誌)|滚石]]》杂志的[[彼得·特拉维斯|彼得·特拉维斯]]称赞了凯斯·理德查兹和杰弗里·拉什的表现，但感觉杰克·斯派罗这个角色的运气也未免有些太好了<ref>{{cite news|author=Peter Travers |title=Pirates of the Caribbean: At World's End |publisher=''Rolling Stone'' |date=2007-05-22 |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/reviews/movie/9474908/review/14756791/pirates_of_the_caribbean_at_worlds_end |accessdate=2009-05-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090501040623/http://www.rollingstone.com/reviews/movie/9474908/review/14756791/pirates_of_the_caribbean_at_worlds_end |archivedate=2009-05-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，他还在之后称本片是2007年最糟糕的电影之一<ref>{{cite web |author=Travers, Peter |date=2007-12-19 |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/news/the-best-and-worst-movies-of-2007-20071227?page=2 |title=Peter Travers' Best and Worst Movies of 2007 |publisher=Rolling Stone |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130823135019/http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/news/the-best-and-worst-movies-of-2007-20071227?page=2 |archive-date=2013-08-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。科尔姆·安德鲁（{{lang|en|Colm Andrew}}）表示电影总体上让人感到失望，其最后的对决中充斥着空洞且无意义的情节、重复的剑术表演和诡计，最后只让人感到无聊<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.iomtoday.co.im/what-s-on/manx-entertainment-news/film-pirates-of-the-caribbean-3-1-1763469 |title=Review by Colm Andrew |publisher=IOM Today |accessdate=2013-08-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130823135536/http://www.iomtoday.co.im/what-s-on/manx-entertainment-news/film-pirates-of-the-caribbean-3-1-1763469 |archivedate=2013-08-23 }}</ref>。

[[周润发|周润发]]的角色在中文媒体中引起了很大的争议，[[香港|香港]]文化杂志《[[瞄|瞄]]》的主编林沛理认为啸风一角和[[傅满洲|傅满洲]]有惊人的相似，他表示傅满洲在阔别好莱坞电影27年后又回来了，只是出于政治正确和营销上的现实角度考虑换了个名字而已<ref>{{cite journal|last=Lam|first=Perry|title=Pirates of the Caribbean: At World's End|journal=Muse Magazine|issue=5|page=73|date=2007年6月}}</ref>。

===票房===
《加勒比海盗3：世界的尽头》在[[北美|北美]]的票房收入为3亿零942万零425美元，其他国家进账6.54亿美元，全球票房达9亿6342万零425美元<ref name="BoxOfficeMojo" />。如果不考虑[[通货膨胀|通货膨胀]]因素，截止2019年7月，这个成绩仍然可以在世界历史电影票房总榜上[[最高電影票房收入列表|名列第45位]]<ref>{{cite web|title=WORLDWIDE GROSSES |work=Box Office Mojo |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/ |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130726070111/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/ |archivedate=2013-07-26 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，也是[[2007年电影|2007年]]票房最高的电影<ref>{{cite web|url=http://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view2=worldwide&yr=2007&p=.htm |title=2007 WORLDWIDE GROSSES |publisher=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-08-23 |deadurl=no |archivedate=2013-05-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130508233318/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view2=worldwide&yr=2007&p=.htm }}</ref>，在已经推出的5部[[加勒比海盗系列电影|加勒比海盗系列电影]]中名列第3位<ref name="POTC-series">{{cite web|url=http://boxofficemojo.com/franchises/chart/?id=piratesofthecaribbean.htm |title=Pirates of the Caribbean Movies at the Box Office |publisher=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-08-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130425023334/http://boxofficemojo.com/franchises/chart/?id=piratesofthecaribbean.htm |archivedate=2013-04-25 }}</ref>。与前作《加勒比海盗2：聚魂棺》相比，本片在北美的收入相对较少，但在其他国家进账要多。全球票房总额落后《加勒比海盗：黑珍珠号的诅咒》和《加勒比海盗2：聚魂棺》约1亿美元<ref name="POTC-series" /><ref>{{cite web|title='Pirates' Vs. 'Pirates' |work=Box Office Mojo |publisher=Amazon.com |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/showdowns/chart/?id=pirates.htm |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130425020736/http://boxofficemojo.com/showdowns/chart/?id=pirates.htm |archivedate=2013-04-25 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。电影在全球上映的首周共计收入3.44亿美元，这个成绩截至2019年7月还可以在历史上的所有电影中排到第21位<ref>{{cite web|title=WORLDWIDE OPENINGS |work=Box Office Mojo |publisher=Amazon.com |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/worldwideopenings.htm |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130801031300/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/worldwideopenings.htm |archivedate=2013-08-01 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

;北美
《加勒比海盗3：世界的尽头》在北美4362家电影院上映，创下了同时上映电影院数量的新纪录<ref>{{cite web|title=Third 'Pirates' Sacks Memorial Record |work=Box Office Mojo |publisher=Amazon.com |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=2321&p=.htm |first=Brandon |last=Gray |date=2007-05-29 |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130509231322/http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=2321&p=.htm |archivedate=2013-05-09 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，放映的银幕数量则有约11500张，截止2013年8月，这个纪录仍然未被打破<ref>{{cite web|title='Harry Potter' Already Breaking Records |work=Box Office Mojo |publisher=Amazon.com |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3208&p=.htm |first=Brandon |last=Gray |date=2011-07-13 |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130514083335/http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3208&p=.htm |archivedate=2013-05-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。其上映前三天就入账1亿1473万2820美元，又以1亿3980万2190美元创下了[[阵亡将士纪念日|阵亡将士纪念日]]周末4天的电影票房新纪录，这个纪录也仍然未被打破<ref>{{cite web|url=http://boxofficemojo.com/alltime/weekends/md.htm |title=All Time Memorial Day Holiday Weekends |publisher=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-08-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130618140403/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/weekends/md.htm |archivedate=2013-06-18 }}</ref>。如果包括[[星期四|星期四]]晚上的预映，《加勒比海盗3：世界的尽头》的5天的时间里收入到达到了1亿5304万2234美元<ref name="BOM">{{cite web|title=Third 'Pirates' Sacks Memorial Record |work=Box Office Mojo |publisher=Amazon.com |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=2321&p=.htm |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130509231322/http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=2321&p=.htm |archivedate=2013-05-09 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，可以在2007年的北美电影票房榜上排到第4位，仅次于《[[蜘蛛人3|蜘蛛人3]]》、《[[史瑞克三世|史瑞克三世]]》和《变形金刚》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?yr=2007&p=.htm |title=2007 DOMESTIC GROSSES |publisher=Amazon.com |work=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-08-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130508222105/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?yr=2007&p=.htm |archivedate=2013-05-08 }}</ref>。其中《蜘蛛侠3》和《史瑞克三世》也都是在5月上映，无论首周票房<ref>{{cite web|title=2007 OPENING GROSSES |work=Box Office Mojo |publisher=Amazon.com |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view=releasedate&view2=opening&yr=2007&p=.htm |accessdate=2011-09-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110623182640/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?yr=2007&view=releasedate&view2=opening&p=.htm |archivedate=2011-06-23 |deadurl=no }}</ref>还是总票房都要超过《加勒比海盗3：世界的尽头》<ref>{{cite web|title=Monthly Box Office |work=Box Office Mojo |publisher=Amazon.com |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/monthly/?view=releasedate&chart=&month=5&yr=2007 |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130513001627/http://boxofficemojo.com/monthly/?view=releasedate&chart=&month=5&yr=2007 |archivedate=2013-05-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。但这很大程度上是因为那两部电影上映较早，所以给本片带来了较大的竞争<ref>{{cite news|title=Third 'Pirates' Sacks Memorial Record |work=Box Office Mojo |publisher=Amazon.com |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=2321&p=.htm |first=Brandon |last=Gray |date=2007-05-29 |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130509231322/http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=2321&p=.htm |archivedate=2013-05-09 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。此外，《加勒比海盗3：世界的尽头》也是加勒比海盗系列电影在北美地区的票房[[亚军|亚军]]<ref name="POTC-series"/>。

;北美以外地区
截止2019年7月，《加勒比海盗3：世界的尽头》还可以在除北美以外其他国家的总票房榜上名列第40位<ref>{{cite news|url=http://boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/?pagenum=1&sort=osgross&order=DESC&p=.htm|title=WORLDWIDE GROSSES|work=Box Office Mojo|publisher=Amazon.com|accessdate=2013-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130510005915/http://boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/?pagenum=1&sort=osgross&order=DESC&p=.htm|archive-date=2013-05-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也是加勒比海盗系列中第二卖座的作品<ref name="POTC-series" />。其上映首周进账约2.16亿美元，这个成绩可以在北美以外地区电影上映首周票房收入历史总榜上排到第15位<ref>{{cite web |title=OVERSEAS TOTAL ALL TIME OPENINGS |work=Box Office Mojo |publisher=Amazon.com |url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/intl/weekend/opening/ |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archive-date=2011-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110623165415/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/intl/weekend/opening/ }}</ref>。影片以1670万美元的成绩创下了[[韩国|韩国]]电影上映首周的票房新纪录，不过这个纪录之后被《[[變形金剛3|變形金剛3]]》超越<ref>{{cite news|title=Around-the-World Roundup: 'Transformers' Lays Waste to World |work=Box Office Mojo |publisher=Amazon.com |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3200&p=.htm |first=Ray |last=Subers |date=2011-07-05 |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130513111713/http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3200&p=.htm |archivedate=2013-05-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。在[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]和[[独联体|独联体]]国家以1400万美元创下同一项目的新纪录<ref>{{cite news|title=Around the World Roundup: 'Sweeney Todd,' Russian Movie Lead |work=Box Office Mojo |publisher=Amazon.com |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=2449&p=.htm |first=Conor |last=Bresnan |date=2008-02-02 |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130509234049/http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=2449&p=.htm |archivedate=2013-05-09 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，还[[西班牙|西班牙]]创下了1190万美元的纪录<ref>{{cite news|title=Around the World Roundup: 'At World's End' Massive in Beginning |work=Box Office Mojo |publisher=Amazon.com |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=2322&p=.htm |first=Conor |last=Bresnan |date=2007-05-30 |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130510021511/http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=2322&p=.htm |archivedate=2013-05-10 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，但之后被《[[海啸奇迹|海啸奇迹]]》超越<ref>{{cite news|title=Around-the-World Roundup: 'Taken 2' Crushes Predecessor, 'Ted' Sets New Record |work=Box Office Mojo |publisher=Amazon.com |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3547&p=.htm |first=Ray |last=Subers |date=2012-10-16 |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130529160637/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3547&p=.htm |archivedate=2013-05-29 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。电影在北美以外的国家连续霸占票房榜冠军宝座3个星期<ref>{{cite web|title=Overseas Total Box Office Index for 2007 |work=Box Office Mojo |publisher=Amazon.com |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/intl/weekend/?yr=2007&currency=us&p=.htm |accessdate=2013-08-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023063556/http://boxofficemojo.com/intl/weekend/?yr=2007&currency=us&p=.htm |archivedate=2012-10-23 }}</ref>。电影上映20天后（2007年6月12日）已经收入5亿美元，打破了《蜘蛛人3》所创以最快速度达到这个成绩的纪录<ref>{{cite news|author=Dave McNary |title='Pirates' tops $500 million overseas |work=Variety |date=2007-06-13 |url=http://variety.com/2007/film/news/pirates-tops-500-million-overseas-1117966859/ |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070616140025/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117966859.html?categoryid=1278&cs=1 |archivedate=2007-06-16 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。除北美外，本片在[[日本|日本]]的收入是最高的，达9110万美元，是《[[阿凡达|阿凡达]]》以前的最后一部在日本上映票房超过10亿[[日元|日元]]的[[好莱坞电影|好莱坞电影]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/alice-gets-10-bil-yen-23919 |title='Alice' gets to 10 bil yen faster than 'Avatar' |first=Gavin |last=Blair |work=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2010-05-24 |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121026115509/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/alice-gets-10-bil-yen-23919 |archivedate=2012-10-26 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，[[英国|英国]]、[[爱尔兰|爱尔兰]]和[[马耳他|马耳他]]以8140万美元紧随其后，第三名则是收入5940万美元的[[德国|德国]]<ref name="Box Office Mojo">{{cite web|title=Pirates of the Caribbean: At World's End (2007) - International Box Office Results |work=Box Office Mojo |publisher=Amazon.com |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=piratesofthecaribbean3.htm |accessdate=2013-08-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130515033322/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=piratesofthecaribbean3.htm |archivedate=2013-05-15 }}</ref>。

===荣誉===
第[[第80屆奧斯卡金像獎|第80屆奧斯卡金像獎]]角逐中，《加勒比海盗3：世界的尽头》获得了化妆和视觉效果两项提名，但最终都没能获奖，分别败给了《玫瑰人生》和《魔幻羅盤》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/80th-winners.html |title=The 80th Academy Awards (2008) Nominees and Winners |publisher=Academy Awards |accessdate=2013-08-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120929190840/http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/80th-winners.html |archivedate=2012-09-29 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。[[艺术指导公会|艺术指导公会]]给予影片奇幻电影奖提名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.adg.org/?art=2007_award |title=Art Directors Guild- Official website –  12th Annual Excellence in Production Design Awards |publisher=Art Directors Guild |accessdate=2013-08-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120722145528/http://www.adg.org/?art=2007_award |archivedate=2012-07-22 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。[[美国作曲家、作家和发行商协会|美国作曲家、作家和发行商协会]]授予汉斯·季默年度电影音乐创作奖和最佳动作/历险电影原创配乐奖<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ascap.com/playback/2008/FALL/FACES_PLACES/filmtv/goldspirit.aspx |title=ASCAP – ASCAP Composers Golden at the GoldSpirit Awards and Úbeda Film Music Conference |publisher=ASCAP |accessdate=2013-08-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121009113916/http://www.ascap.com/playback/2008/FALL/FACES_PLACES/filmtv/goldspirit.aspx |archivedate=2012-10-09 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。电影获得了[[英国电影学院奖|英国电影学院奖]]最佳特技效果奖提名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bafta.org/awards/film/nominations/?year=2007 |title=BAFTA Film Nominations 2007 |publisher=BAFTA |accessdate=2011-06-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111118095253/http://www.bafta.org/awards/film/nominations/?year=2007 |archivedate=2011-11-18 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。服装设计师公会也给予影片奇幻电影卓越服装设计奖提名<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.variety.com/awardcentral_article/VR1117979163.html?nav=news&categoryid=1983&cs=1 |title=Costume Designers unveil nominees |work=Variety |date=2008-01-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121108130711/http://www.variety.com/awardcentral_article/VR1117979163.html?nav=news&categoryid=1983&cs=1 |archivedate=2012-11-08 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2012-11-08 |author=McCarthy, Libby }}</ref>。

电影在[[2008年MTV電影大獎|2008年MTV電影大獎]]上获得了3项提名，強尼·戴普最后夺得了最佳喜剧表演奖<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/ontv/movieawards/2008/ |title=2008 MTV Movie Awards |publisher=MTV |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130812035553/http://www.mtv.com/ontv/movieawards/2008/ |archivedate=2013-08-12 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。在第34届[[人民选择奖|人民选择奖]]上影片获得5项提名，并拿下了最受欢迎电影、最受欢迎续集，最受欢迎男影星（強尼·戴普）和最受欢迎女动作影星<ref>{{cite news|title=The People's Choice Awards Winners! |publisher=ComingSoon.net |date=2008-01-09 |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=40795 |accessdate=2013-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121001064858/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=40795 |archivedate=2012-10-01 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。此外影片还在[[青少年选择奖|青少年选择奖]]中获6项提名，最终有5项获奖，2008年[[尼克频道儿童选择奖|尼克频道儿童选择奖]]中也有3项提名，最终赢得了最受欢迎电影男演员奖<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hellomovies.com/awards/pirates-of-the-caribbean-at-world-s-end |title=HelloMovies – Pirates of the Caribbean award list |publisher=Hellomovies.com |accessdate=2011-06-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090621014312/http://www.hellomovies.com/awards/pirates-of-the-caribbean-at-world-s-end |archivedate=2009-06-21 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

